t-3303966">与 Queen and the Foos 一起在《We Will Rock You》中担任主唱</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-struts-announce-fourth-album-pretty-vicious-3481229">The Struts 宣布第四张专辑《Pretty Vicious》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
