ucks">Knucks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy">Romy</a> ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-xx">The xx</a> )。</p><p>今天（8 月 10 日），组织者在下周开始的音乐节之前将最后一批艺术家添加到 APE &#39;23 法案中。</p><p>加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a>和公司。下周五将有尼日利亚歌手兼制作人 Tay Iwar、创作型歌手 Tamera、伦敦歌手兼制作人 Natanya 以及​​新兴 R&amp;B 艺术家 Trebla。</p><p>接下来的一周，The Strokes 将得到澳大利亚<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/azure-ryder">Azure Ryder</a> 、英国另类摇滚乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/feet">Feet</a>和利兹四人组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lobjectif">L&#39;Objectif 的</a>支持。 </p><figure id="attachment_3280006" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3280006" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3280006" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images.jpg" alt="The Strokes 乐队的 Julian Casablancas 在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Julian-Casablancas-of-The-Strokes.-Credit-Matt-JelonekGetty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3280006" class="wp-caption-text"> The Strokes 乐队的朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯 (Julian Casablancas) 进行现场表演。图片来源：Matt Jelonek/Getty Images</figcaption><